      • arccos

        public double arccos​(double num)
        This method calculate arccosine of given number. If argument is from domain [-1,1], then return the arc cosine of an angle in range of [0,pi] of a value([-1,1]) and return the value in range of [0,pi]. If argument is from outside domain, then the result is NaN.
        Parameters:
        num - the value whose arc cosine is to be returned.
        Returns:
        the arccosine of the given number.
